{"hbca923a4g4a49g4267gac8cgec9945411a44": ["You're here. Just like it told me you'd be, gith.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "2b481e3d-02f2-4ad9-e78b-3c88d45f3d49"], "h20e0ce3bg8aceg4fa8gbb65g9c09297b9901": ["*Your mind rushes into hers - a storm of desperation, confusion and a will other than her own.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "40c0f227-8df9-aa3c-b50e-26bc45214bb4"], "h69cb01c3g2863g4935g8002g0f76904734e4": ["It took me so long to find you. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "ec6dead7-24f4-b79e-4540-d079512238a7"], "hd172287cgff01g4ae7gb8fcg5e59bc787e45": ["What's wrong? You seem different than before.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "5f1a4434-fec5-0404-ec55-d238b7ff9829"], "hededa973gf86ag494cgb532g30d7114048b4": ["No questions! I can't... concentrate with all these voices! Just <i>listen</i>.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "b15503b6-75b0-34e3-9d6d-a6d3008e2918"], "hf1f6d5a5g84c8g4228gb559gb25248dee96d": ["The whispering won't let me sleep. It keeps pushing me - to you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "7dcc819f-ebf3-7c4a-9369-759f35d2e477"], "ha0aca5fcg26eag45a7gad62gf8f93ba13014": ["Even when I'm awake, I dream. There's blood, there's so much blood.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c6287406-ca3e-66e3-a751-edafe9edd484"], "hb27039b4g6367g4a17g87d9g838ee05bc370": ["I can't sleep. The whispering won't let me. It keeps pushing me - to you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "362e2dbb-21f3-5fa7-904e-4549672e2da9"], "h3109256dg4f09g4367g8e08g83d4a3cb063f": ["The ravings of a lunatic. Strike her down.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "9c4f78b8-06d5-3b13-3511-3398ff0ac9a4"], "ha4f96cacg5afag4a09g8b54gaebdb8049a9b": ["*There is a knife hidden in her belt. Her fingers twitch towards the hilt, ready to draw the blade.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "4d12a40c-5022-82a6-6690-357a8cc3d521"], "hf03b6131g797eg46bega1d1ge3e6acd05ba7": ["I said who are you? Tell me right now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "d6328719-2a2c-2693-b0d9-48aefc4bd030"], "hcd90a785g5083g4389gabd3g485862de2269": ["You know who I am - you saw inside my head. <i>Shadowheart</i>. We were on the ship together.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "baeb8c09-ab33-56e0-77ff-ab5ce5073071"], "h7f95730ag7c3bg4d1cg8de4g2be76e003ad3": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "16c36501-888a-3737-4828-efb9f103df36"], "h3fc73f00g31f5g4fedg8e9eg5ef373d4d4fd": ["Keep your hands away from that blade.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "d926c94d-7f7b-7caf-178d-3cf44013d1b9"], "hf83e94b4g0196g4fc3g8648gad4aa60ec425": ["I keep thinking about the knife going deep. It's the only thing they want me to see.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "9d167008-25d7-3069-be4e-cc5d37534d42"], "h79bc0ed5g987bg49a7ga3d9gbff7ca1a2879": ["And I think they'll stop once I deal with you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "dc37ef53-d86d-03c4-3a82-0c1616945c98"], "hf79d433ag2a98g4b2egab03g3b09597e72cc": ["You can't kill me just because some 'whispers' told you to.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "6ddd631b-c273-722e-c985-f711fbaf28cb"], "h227e7b01g0dedg4175g845dg5653c7e1c575": ["I can't see anything else! I can't shake it.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "978b13e5-750a-4437-d6b4-be0e78409176"], "h9b1a1046gaabfg4d97ga6fcge25100279ced": ["The whispering's already quieter here. Once you're dead, it'll be gone entirely.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "d9402272-206a-276b-82b8-9cd976ea8286"], "had814695gbc5fg4e72g8ef4gadad1da28f45": ["Threaten me again, and it'll be the last thing you do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3d9eb2ae-2df0-fb9d-fe79-21d70c0fb7b1"], "h3a659ca1g514bg44d3g98c9gd35b3eb7584c": ["What else do I do? My head is splitting open. I can't leave. I can't!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "9ac39ae6-dd63-7df1-2b70-8a974c4413a4"], "h6a85ba50g09c9g44d2ga9ddg7abf580f0e0b": ["You can certainly try.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c3355207-564d-8721-bd44-e60d43a9e178"], "h0d98b0f5ge2f0g4c3bg82d7g51e967fa6f19": ["Threaten me again, and it'll be the last thing you do.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "9fca837f-c2ca-a283-8848-8bf2f8115f38"], "h2f27a563g165bg4d29gbf55g48a1b53a7f47": ["You're exhausted - not thinking straight. You need to rest. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "aaac78e4-34cf-41db-4eb6-d38096c8c99d"], "h7685e39ega4b5g45f3g85c0g45c708a9ea24": ["Rest where? I can't leave. The whispers won't let me leave.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "092b07d1-19bc-acbf-1fff-a63ae2849955"], "h7a88eac9g2183g423egac9cg93c2df818fe6": ["You can stay here. I'll watch over you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3ae09b08-1e37-e1c8-df2b-c55b6e9484c6"], "h7bf1ab3dg916fg481fgbc02g1e3a898aef3c": ["Stay. I can stay.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "876525e4-8735-3582-3e5a-ea096586cb3c"], "h45d61e41g52afg4164g99c8gc4e1763abbb2": ["It's a little quieter now. Is that what they wanted?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "434193f5-f473-7e93-f764-90a3e59b61b1"], "h2a85cd55gb187g4ee6gacbcg024ccdd69b82": ["I am surrounded by <i>madness.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "f9bb3cd8-24b6-c296-841c-db6fec135025"], "h69f30c9agb2b5g4c29gac29g26cd27f63dc0": ["|Karlach reaction|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "9c6ba38c-ab83-f009-08ac-0c47a185d15d"], "h4f259771g6a6bg40acgb388ged45dda36afc": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "fda392bc-3157-dc2f-4cf5-5459c76bb5e5"], "h54a6cfa4g557fg416fg8f9dg98bc9423e32f": ["Some day that soft heart of yours is going to be torn out of your chest.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c29e8e62-d76d-9686-3665-ce11d991acec"], "hc2fccb45g95bfg45cdgb8e2g924ad305299f": ["_", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "a35887f1-e2d5-a854-acf7-d18b9c2fff7b"], "hb1a84415g63e2g4751gbfb7g0ff140015290": ["Are you feeling all right, miss? Maybe a lie-down's in order...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "805bd75b-7790-42c0-85cc-eee0dc648bcb"], "h9c98d4f5ga8dfg452bgb17fg9b9375c17fde": ["She needs sleep. And she needs to be closely guarded.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "aa9460bc-8311-e6f4-d141-c8039d20489a"], "h90553c46g4f9eg40bcgb634ga2119dedf26d": ["I can't risk having you around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3e5e1776-a916-4e0f-5ec8-789b3aa25e60"], "h96d1ca3cg5797g486bgbbe8gbe514f385c3f": ["Oh, you've risked plenty.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "105c0d14-6c9c-48b7-71ec-18797626a020"], "h4d0532edg31ebg4dbcga6b8g994f79b3792d": ["No. Enough talk. Enough voices.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "8b752880-555b-6025-8e0b-255156950127"], "h6c2d3cddga40dg4cb1g968fg6ef9bae93a89": ["There's something controlling your mind. I can feel it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "143e7cb3-59e5-7683-c062-c809519a3a23"], "h60706147g5db0g40c0g8a22gd03d76882bc0": ["Then how do I make them stop? What do I do?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "42ce3263-c796-da7e-c990-201de9ec9f64"], "h766504fcg7033g4d79gaf10gefb68a3ac26e": ["<i>Attack her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "59afaf2a-1fa7-96a6-4e8b-1bb091a03ec4"], "hea20cc9fgdd18g49f1g8c95g063f94176bb4": ["Don't do anything rash. There has to be an explanation for this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "815d7c16-24d8-8a61-323c-889b57eaa6d7"], "ha57ac191g4cf4g4ec5ga545gc8d5adf68c1d": ["I don't want explanations. I want sleep.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "e78a9946-10f1-8e44-890a-de2bfe1984fe"], "h2a6bfcd5g8d2fg4d37g8ab5g78601a000f8c": ["You're not dealing with anyone. You're leaving - now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "d83fad3e-d749-deed-aa40-79704ffe319b"], "h8e10222bgd497g4595g99a5g91d5f8045f11": ["No. I'm where I need to be.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "ddd10661-91e3-5461-3154-d696006cae35"], "hcb8fb34eg1ddag448egb2ebged28109a298e": ["Slow down - what whispering?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "b5bbd4c6-45f0-75f3-3350-7ac681c75be4"], "h20189425geeb7g49abg9558gde5bcd71bc67": ["They've been in my head ever since... it doesn't matter. They brought me here.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "408e9d93-31c9-1e9e-0dcb-21243f942778"], "h72155248geff2g48b5g8723ga1f56c3bb923": ["There's something controlling your mind. I can feel it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "fb7b9bc4-8b1a-a7c6-91fd-e19d5d891879"], "h27cdf129ge79dg4cd9gabafg6cf855c4b228": ["Then how do I make them stop? What do I do?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "4d7e5b79-46e1-a38d-111a-c51a463a18d0"], "hc6c3d1f4gaccfg4239ga53bgb24090a92898": ["<i>Is the parasite compelling her to do this? Delve into her mind.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "09f9b58c-c4a0-861e-b312-807ed152c33c"], "hdb22dc77gf224g437fg920dg373b7e0434cd": ["*Not her tadpole - a chorus of harsh, relentless whispers in her head.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "fa98f82c-7481-7450-e657-e5f8a5f458ac"], "hc43da2b6gae05g47deg8af0g6800ea5ca69a": ["Get out of my head! <i>All of you!</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "98b3877d-7412-ec3b-96f2-8f283883462b"], "hf8ef72d4gb971g4f0agaaa9gaef18830931d": ["I'm tired of being <i>pushed.</i>", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "a0616acb-c73c-c54f-b38b-22d08c647592"], "h2b85f229g5548g4c70gb263gb74d30dd6225": ["<i>Stare her down.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "09e24698-3265-30a9-cc0c-0b2dec4d3723"], "hd74af99egedeeg4bb7gb1e6ge679f62ad78c": ["Don't look at me like that. I can't... no.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "0193b5e2-dc64-c062-bd26-348cdd041c32"], "h58b62a26g464fg4cdbga897g1df57e98f4f9": ["Say what you have to say.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "4358bfae-62df-b2c2-b18c-5deade473733"], "h78ce4e69g1af3g400aga394g538336a64cb9": ["You're not yourself - something's interfering with your thoughts. I can feel it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "a794f4e1-1878-9dbd-c389-6493365ca09d"], "h47bd7e63gb1d6g4b93ga13fgf9c2c8ae7db9": ["Maybe you're right. But the whispers won't stop.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "b31ba055-d1d6-74cb-202d-5e062fc44ea9"], "h3c9d437ag926ag4cd0gbec2g49acb83803b0": ["Now... now what do I do?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "8d13a5e2-c85b-632c-d2da-7946b88a4eef"], "h732b4d7cg4119g4edegbda4g83937baae6bc": ["You can stay here. I'll watch over you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3601241f-42ba-d374-9dec-129c3563662c"], "h21f32e6cg188cg450dga14bg2fa7f53e6800": ["Hurting me won't help you. Put down the blade.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "ce5a7d5a-beb6-18f7-f0ee-536c8f6035ae"], "hccd646a9g1972g4f89gbaadgd17099450989": ["I <i>can't</i>.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "f397e376-fa1c-e35e-ea60-edce407f2e48"], "h3e5cf58agb0a9g4d65g8772g14783ad93823": ["You're hallucinating. The blade isn't real.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "5dd6a9f3-4d31-2e42-1c16-ec43010fd392"], "h253fd219gd0f9g44d7g8007g06abbaeca3df": ["It's not? What are these voices doing to me?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "1fdbed15-0288-1241-54b2-63576f1db153"], "h49e1535eg786bg4f98g8166g737fb634b959": ["Liar. <i>Liar.</i> Liar!", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "dcf7e95f-7d6d-0d50-a78b-17040bde31c8"], "h649d1fbbg276cg426cgb745g6859adfdcf6a": ["<i>Attack her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "42008e28-55bb-6dad-c116-ce157d74905d"], "h20048de7g1c13g4e33gbc20g5ec03f67fad8": ["There we go. Clean and deep.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "e32ab7e5-bc98-cc7e-8898-91b2d6cbe360"], "he8ca9f5agd832g4911ga9a4g552d88497afe": ["<i>Stare her down.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "d567a6cf-ac18-cfdb-8995-c378b334565e"], "h2d2ad8abga4c3g444cg8992g4e4401bab9a3": ["I'm not pushing. Let's just talk this over.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "434967b3-cc9c-b988-8b8c-a87f2eba3559"], "h5bdd1cb9g2faag4286ga8aeg7698dd7cf847": ["Bleed for me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "8b54e59a-87fe-f278-8bc9-56edae6a27e9"], "he8ce5ba8g6b96g48f9gb0e3g7eb4ac5cc8e7": ["<i>Use your connection to her. Delve into her thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "08d1f61a-a9ec-b3f9-3167-e606563f7470"], "hdd08feb1g3693g4216g9986gbbfe2e47e6ea": ["*A strange miasma clings to her thoughts. Not the tadpole, but your interruption fazes her.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "1205165d-bddd-8ae6-6944-657acd7e2a30"], "h2aa821b7g15a1g46dag9c79g308fd592f734": ["Your stance is off. Lower the blade before I take it from you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3bd44a37-2533-a97a-5b67-b573809611c1"], "h197a919bg3094g4fbdg81efg728756d30f1f": ["|Karlach get rid of her/hear her out|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "5d249b24-8dd7-c728-7559-d848f0914c3f"], "h283fadefg1024g42d9g9887g591926b6846c": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "a9819267-c96c-b1ca-c50d-a8469d217fd5"], "h0a972525gfc99g48dcgb8edgadbd9f45d0f4": ["It sounds like death would be a mercy. Let's deliver it.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c20c3eb7-63e9-655a-d1e4-2f4de70907a6"], "h2a079996g10c4g407cg8132g9c0c61ef3b1b": ["_", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "ee98e095-e23f-a0fd-4a21-98fcd5cba66b"], "h3c4a24a0g35f8g47e0ga56dgf124a480354d": ["Whispering? Her brain's been bugged too.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c48e835b-b3b3-b19d-3752-761c14625806"], "he2199212gc803g41a1gbabfg213c05b770bb": ["Careful! She's about to lash out.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3d8c07ee-2250-b0d4-de82-9dce6dd69593"], "h6c6cce0aga11cg46acg8f57g7791b558628b": ["Hold up - who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "c490ac9f-b80a-df24-4695-3b9aca99c92b"], "h24330a4ag4932g49e2g9ebdg9cf93bbef94a": ["Quiet! I can't... concentrate with all these voices! Just <i>listen</i>.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "906741e7-b88f-0773-0a37-ee387b89810f"], "h1b7e86beg032eg48b3g8afcg097dd5716e51": ["What is this? Have you been tracking me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "3de27b21-a856-3dde-4b1b-84aace4276f9"], "he1452b7dgd937g4a89g8b78g5ef013773822": ["You're infected, same as me. How did you get here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "4ad5334d-7ab8-9147-7a51-c4c6f6e6d317"], "h61cb9f92gad83g4b74g90cag92422df18c49": ["<i>Say nothing and observe Shadowheart closely.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "58fc59ff-ec72-4599-78f5-7cc9f80eb49c"], "hce42ab63gcc90g4f10ga0dag2fd6fe0181a9": ["<i>Say nothing and watch the intruder closely.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "982d8fd6-b3d1-618f-db45-222d025f2ac0"], "h7ed8d327gd5fcg46ccg9dcag0359ae1b24cd": ["You're here. Just like it told me. And with a gith - I should have figured.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "6884141c-7fa5-e4be-c9b8-385add4d5320"], "hf099d4degaf52g4360gbbc0g6ce314d70fb8": ["You're here. Just like it told me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "4fb5ebc0-19de-81cd-62c6-bf2439c9ebcd"], "h2d3d24e8gfc91g4174g8cabg287b4a3d13f0": ["You're here. Just like it told me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "0bc4f1de-820f-ab62-e455-221f71ef9d17"], "h9c6fe611g8d24g46d7g8791g7d6c174b72c9": ["The whispers won't let me sleep. They keep pushing me - to you.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "cb01de24-78b1-de16-9111-6ff806738019"], "h7bd28d8dg8710g4d55g8c7ag11e86f72566d": ["But if you're dead... maybe it'll go away.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Shadowheart_CFM_Ultimatum.html", "6afc05f2-ea7e-ae31-29dd-a3474013f32c"]}